20Bankman-Fried%20is%20incarcerated%20while%20appealing%20his%20criminal%20conviction%2C%20is%20equipped%20with%20video%20teleconferencing%20equipment%20typically%20used%20for%20inmates%20to%20communicate%20with%20their%20lawyers.%20A%20representative%20for%20the%20jail%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Bankman-Fried's%20interview%20with%20Carlson%20but%20said%20that%20video%20interviews%20can%20be%20arranged%20with%20members%20of%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20Carlson%20talked%20about%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d0a21b4-2354-49f5-aedb-0d7aa70daa1f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHanging%20out%20with%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20the%2040-minute%20interview%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20called%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20Combs%20%26quot%3Btwo%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20prisoners%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20asking%20Bankman-Fried%20what%20it's%20like%20living%20in%20such%20close%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20only%20seen%20one%20piece%20of%20him%2C%20which%20is%20Diddy%20in%20prison.%20He's%20been%20kind%20to%20people%20in%20the%20unit.%20He's%20been%20kind%20to%20me.%20It's%20a%20position%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20be%20in.%20Obviously%2C%20he%20doesn't%2C%20I%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20soul%20crushing%20place%20for%20the%20world%20in%20general%2C%20and%20what%20we%20see%20are%20just%20the%20people%20that%20are%20around%20us%20on%20the%20inside%20rather%20than%20who%20we%20are%20on%20the%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20also%20said%20that%20other%20inmates%20have%20challenged%20his%20chess%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20good%20at%20chess.%20That's%20one%20thing%20I%20learned%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20told%20Carlson.%20%26quot%3BFormer%20armed%20robbers%20who%20don't%20speak%20English%20and%20probably%20didn't%20graduate%20middle%20school%20%E2%80%94%20a%20surprising%20number%20are%20surprisingly%20good%20at%20chess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c073f36-6c32-4a96-8d50-45ba6429d96c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20unflagging%20passage%20of%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20turned%2033%20on%20Thursday%20but%20downplayed%20the%20milestone%20to%20Carlson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20tell%20Diddy%20it's%20your%20birthday%20tomorrow%3F%20I%20don't%20believe%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20joked%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20which%20was%20apparently%20filmed%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20else%20might%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20says%20he%20expects%20to%20be%20in%20his%20late%2040s%20when%20released%20from%20prison%20%E2%80%94%20if%20he's%20not%20pardoned%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Carlson%20asked%20whether%20he%20thinks%20he'll%20make%20it%20that%20long%2C%20the%20ex-crypto%20mogul%20said%20he%20didn't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f7fd955-2954-4d1e-a866-e67955ade208%5C%22%3EJail%20economics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20with%20no%20money%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20cryptocurrency%20%E2%80%94%20inmates%20use%20muffins%20as%20a%20medium%20of%20exchange%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20said%20he%20hoards%20muffins%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmuffin%20economy%26quot%3B%20but%20doesn't%20eat%20them.%20He%20sticks%20to%20rice%20and%20beans%20and%20ramen%20noodles%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20everything%20is%20so%20diminished%20in%20prison%2C%20you%20see%20people%20fighting%20over%20a%20single%20banana%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e7ebe1c-6de4-4c8b-92f2-814cd42c1a27%5C%22%3ECrypto%20policy%20under%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidency%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20overseen%20far%20friendlier%20crypto%20policies%20than%20former%20Pr