y%20and%20deliberately%26quot%3B%20hit%20by%20the%20vehicle%20of%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20just%20a%20day%20after%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20directed%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20also%20to%20register%20FIRs%20based%20on%20the%20complaints%20of%20the%20agitating%20students%20of%20the%20university%20instead%20of%20just%20acting%20on%20the%20complaints%20from%20Trinamool%20Congress-affiliated%20West%20Bengal%20College%20%26amp%3B%20University%20Professors'%20Association%20(WBCUPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20accused%20under%20various%20charges%20like%20physical%20assault%2C%20giving%20threats%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20satisfaction%20with%20the%20development%2C%20Amit%20Roy%2C%20father%20of%20the%20two%20injured%20students%2C%20Indranuj%20Roy%20said%20that%20in%20a%20democratic%20country%2C%20the%20work%20of%20the%20police%20administration%20is%20to%20follow%20democratic%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20is%20not%20done%20it%20is%20against%20democratic%20practices.%20The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20order%20on%20Wednesday%20directing%20the%20police%20also%20to%20file%20FIRs%20based%20on%20the%20complaints%20of%20the%20students%2C%20is%20proof%20of%20why%20people%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Roy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20besides%20directing%20the%20police%20to%20register%20FIRs%20based%20on%20the%20complaints%20of%20the%20students%2C%20Justice%20Tirthankar%20Ghosh%20also%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruckus%20broke%20out%20within%20the%20university%20campus%20on%20Saturday%20when%20the%20Minister's%20car%20was%20allegedly%20stopped%20after%20it%20entered%20the%20campus%2C%20and%20a%20scuffle%20followed.%20The%20students%20were%20demanding%20immediate%20elections%20for%20the%20university's%20st