imposition%20of%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20goods.%20Lawson%20Whiting%2C%20CEO%20of%20Brown-Forman%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Jack%20Daniel's%2C%20has%20denounced%20the%20Canadian%20retaliation%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20that's%20worse%20than%20a%20tariff%2C%20because%20it's%20literally%20taking%20your%20sales%20away%2C%20completely%20removing%20our%20products%20from%20the%20shelves%2C%26quot%3B%20Whiting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Liquor%20Control%20Board%20of%20Ontario%20(LCBO)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20alcohol%20buyers%2C%20removed%20US-made%20drinks%20from%20its%20shelves%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ontario%20Premier%20Doug%20Ford%20revealed%20that%20the%20LCBO%20sells%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20US%20alcohol%20annually%2C%20emphasising%20that%20all%20these%20products%20are%20now%20off%20the%20shelves.%20The%20LCBO's%20exclusive%20wholesaler%20status%20in%20Ontario%20means%20that%20other%20retailers%2C%20bars%2C%20and%20restaurants%20in%20the%20province%20can%20no%20longer%20restock%20US%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20retaliated%20against%20the%20US%20tariffs%20with%20its%20own%2025%25%20levies%20on%20American%20goods%2C%20including%20beer%2C%20spirits%2C%20and%20wine.%20Some%20provinces%2C%20such%20as%20Ontario%20and%20Nova%20Scotia%2C%20have%20taken%20additional%20measures.%20The%20trade%20tensions%20have%20sparked%20a%20nationalist%20sentiment%20among%20Canadians%2C%20with%20some%20opting%20to%20buy%20local%20products%20instead%20of%20US-made%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhiting%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20Canada%20accounts%20for%20only%201%25%20of%20the%20company's%20total%20sales%2C%20making%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20trade%20dispute%20manageable.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20is%20also%20monitoring%20developments%20in%20Mexico%2C%20which%20accounted%20for%207%25%20of%20its%20sales%20in%202024%20and%20has%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20US%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20dispute%20has%20drawn%20strong%20reactions%20from%20Canadian%20leaders.%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20criticised%20the%20US%20tariffs%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20dumb%20thing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20accused%20President%20Trump%20of%20seeking%20to%20undermine%20the%20Canadian%20economy.%20Canada's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20Trump's%20remarks%20about%20making%20Canada%20the%2051st%20US%20state%2C%20taking%20them%20%26quot%3Bvery%20seriously%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741284480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F19qr5028_lawson-whiting_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjack-daniels-ceo-says-canada-pulling-us-alcohol-worse-than-tariff-7864939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawson%20Whiting%2C%20CEO%20of%20Brown-Forman%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Jack%20Daniel's%2C%20has%20denounced%20the%20Canadian%20retaliation%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20levies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20reveals%20her%20father%20Mahesh%20Bhatt's%20advice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741284380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118767636%2Cimgsize-23842.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-reveals-her-father-mahesh-bhatts-advice-id-rather-be-stupid-%2Farticleshow%2F118767629.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin