6quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20stood%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20comments%20following%20earlier%20talks%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20who%20he%20accused%20of%20using%20the%20dispute%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20in%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20Thursday%20that%20Ottawa%20will%20remain%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20with%20Washington%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20foreseeable%20future%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bbreaks%20for%20certain%20sectors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20remains%20to%20get%20these%20tariffs%2C%20all%20tariffs%20removed%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20markets%20tumbled%20after%20Trump's%2025%20percent%20tariffs%20on%20US%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20took%20effect%20Tuesday%20and%20economists%20say%20Americans%20are%20likely%20to%20face%20broad-based%20price%20rises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States'%20expanded%20reprieve%20for%20Mexico%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20White%20House%20gave%20automakers%20temporary%20relief%20too%20from%20the%20levies%20that%20hit%20everything%20from%20lumber%20to%20avocado%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecord%20deficit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20office%20in%20January%2C%20Trump%20has%20made%20a%20series%20of%20tariff%20threats%20on%20allies%20and%20adversaries%20alike%2C%20declaring%20trade%20wars%20will%20be%20a%20key%20part%20of%20his%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20justified%20the%20tariffs%20on%20the%20United%20States'%20two%20giant%20neighbors%20and%20vital%20trade%20partners%2C%20along%20with%20China%2C%20as%20a%20way%20to%20stop%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20trafficking%20of%20the%20deadly%20drug%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Canada%20contributes%20less%20than%20one%20percent%20of%20fentanyl%20to%20the%20United%20States'%20illicit%20supply%2C%20according%20to%20Canadian%20and%20US%20government%20data.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20relatively%20minor%20source%20of%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20compared%20to%20flows%20across%20the%20Mexican%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20pushed%20back%20on%20US%20allegations%20of%20its%20role%20in%20the%20fentanyl%20supply%20chain%2C%20calling%20this%20a%20domestic%20issue%20that%20tariffs%20will%20not%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20tariffs%20should%20become%20a%20major%20source%20of%20US%20government%20revenue%2C%20while%20remedying%20trade%20imbalances%20and%20practices%20Washington%20deems%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20trade%20deficit%20surged%20to%20a%20new%20record%20in%20January%20according%20to%20government%20data%20Thursday%2C%20as%20imports%20spiked%20while%20tariff%20worries%20flared%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Trump's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20trade%20gap%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20ballooned%2034%20percent%20to%20%24131.4%20billion%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%2010%20percent%20jump%20in%20imports%20for%20the%20month%2C%20said%20the%20Commerce%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20widest%20deficit%20for%20a%20month%20on%20record%2C%20dating%20back%20to%201992%2C%20and%20the%20expansion%20was%20more%20than%20analysts%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETariff%20jitters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20the%20US%20deficit%20was%20likely%20bolstered%20by%20gold%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bstripping%20out%20this%20impact%2C%20all%20other%20imports%20rose%205.5%20percent%2C%20indicating%20front-loading%20of%20shipments%20was%20in%20full%20swing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Oxford%20Economics%20senior%20economist%20Matthew%20Martin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20refers%20to%20a%20tendency%20for%20businesses%20to%20try%20and%20get%20ahead%20of%20additional%20costs%20from%20potential%20tariffs%2C%20and%20possible%20supply%20chain%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconom