have%20been%20placed%20in%20a%20qualifying%20group%20alongside%20Bangladesh%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20Singapore%20for%20the%20Asian%20Cup.%20In%20the%20tournament's%20previous%20edition%2C%20India%20had%20a%20disappointing%20run%2C%20failing%20to%20progress%20past%20the%20group%20stage%20after%20losing%20all%20their%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%2026-member%20squad%20for%20March%202025%20FIFA%20International%20Window%3A%20Goalkeepers%3A%20Amrinder%20Singh%2C%20Gurmeet%20Singh%2C%20Vishal%20Kaith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefenders%3A%20Asish%20Rai%2C%20Boris%20Singh%20Thangjam%2C%20Chinglensana%20Singh%20Konsham%2C%20Hmingthanmawia%2C%20Mehtab%20Singh%2C%20Rahul%20Bheke%2C%20Roshan%20Singh%2C%20Sandesh%20Jhingan%2C%20Subhasish%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMidfielders%3A%20Ashique%20Kuruniyan%2C%20Ayush%20Dev%20Chhetri%2C%20Brandon%20Fernandes%2C%20Brison%20Fernandes%2C%20Jeakson%20Singh%20Thounaojam%2C%20Lalengmawia%2C%20Liston%20Colaco%2C%20Mahesh%20Singh%20Naorem%2C%20Suresh%20Singh%20Wangjam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForwards%3A%20Sunil%20Chhetri%2C%20Farukh%20Choudhary%2C%20Irfan%20Yadwad%2C%20Lallianzuala%20Chhangte%2C%20Manvir%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741278780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fm78ea638_sc_650x400_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fsunil-chhetri-returns-to-national-team-for-fifa-international-window-in-march-indian-football-body-confirms-7864158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legendary%20striker%20Sunil%20Chhetri%20will%20make%20a%20surprising%20return%20to%20the%20national%20team%2C%20confirmed%20the%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22