A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0mwllzzyxlo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0mwllzzyxlo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Popular%20Painkiller%20Shows%20Surprising%20Potential%20To%20Prevent%20Cancer%20Spread%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprising%20breakthrough%2C%20experts%20have%20found%20that%20a%20common%20painkiller%2C%20aspirin%2C%20could%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20preventing%20the%20spread%20of%20cancer.%20Researchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20discovered%20how%20aspirin%20may%20help%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20some%20types%20of%20cancer%20by%20potentially%20stopping%20them%20from%20metastasising.%20This%20groundbreaking%20finding%20could%20offer%20an%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20option%20in%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20as%20previous%20studies%20suggested%20that%20aspirin%20could%20enhance%20the%20immune%20system's%20ability%20to%20target%20and%20eliminate%20harmful%20cancer%20cells.%20The%20team's%20discovery%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20cancer%20research%2C%20offering%20hope%20for%20more%20effective%20treatment%20options%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jie%20Yang%2C%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2025%2F03%2F05%2Fscientists-eureka-moment-widely-used-pill-help-prevent-cancer-spread-22670491%2F%3Fito%3Darticle.app.share.top.whatsapp%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Metro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20discovery%20was%20'a%20Eureka%20moment'%2C%20as%20before%20this%20the%20scientists%20were%20not%20'aware%20of%20the%20implication%20of%20our%20findings%20in%20understanding%20the%20anti-metastatic%20activity%20of%20aspirin.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4n119xr7o%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20report%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20aspirin%20disrupts%20the%20platelets%20and%20removes%20their%20influence%20over%20the%20T-cells%20so%20they%20can%20hunt%20out%20the%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf%20Rahul%20Roychoudhuri%2C%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20discovered%20is%20that%20aspirin%20might%20work%2C%20surprisingly%2C%20by%20unleashing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20immune%20system%20to%20recognise%20and%20kill%20metastasising%20cancer%20cells.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20thinks%20the%20drug%20would%20work%20best%20in%20cancers%20that%20have%20been%20caught%20early%20and%20could%20be%20used%20after%20treatment%2C%20such%20as%20surgery%2C%20to%20help%20the%20immune%20system%20find%20any%20cancer%20that%20might%20already%20have%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20cancer%20patient%2C%20don't%20rush%20to%20your%20local%20pharmacy%20to%20buy%20aspirin%20just%20yet%2C%20but%20actively%20consider%20participation%20in%20ongoing%20or%20upcoming%20trials%20of%20aspirin%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Prof%20Mangesh%20Thorat%2C%20a%20surgeon%20and%20cancer%20researcher%20at%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20the%20study%20provided%20%26quot%3Bthe%20missing%20piece%20of%20the%20jigsaw%20puzzle%26quot%3B%20in%20understanding%20how%20aspirin%20works%2C%20but%20there%20were%20still%20questions%20to%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20there%20is%20risk...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4n119xr7o%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20report%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Esuggests%20that%20aspirin%20can%20cause%20dangerous%20internal%20bleeding%2C%20including%20strokes%2C%20so%20the%20risks%20have%20to%20be%20balanced.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20effect%20works%20for%20all%20cancers%20or%20just%20specific%20ones.%20And%20this%20is%20still%20animal%20research%2C%20so%20while%20the%20scientists%20think%20this%20would%20apply%20to%20people%2C%20that%20will%20still%20need%20to%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20patients%20-%20with%20Lynch%20syndrome%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20cancers%20-%20are%20already%20recommended%20aspirin.%20But%20it%20will%20still%20take%20proper%20clinical%20trials%20to%20understand%20whether%20more%20patients%20would%20benefit%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741273140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmm8lg7vo_how-aspirin-could-help-stop-cancer-from-returning_625x300_06_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Faspirin-popular-painkiller-shows-surprising-potential-to-prevent-cancer-spread-7863881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20suggests%20that%20aspirin%2C%20a%20common%20painkiller%2C%20may%20help%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20cancer%20by%20boosting%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20offering%20hope%20for%20more%20affordable%20treatment%20options%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Faspirin-popular-painkiller-shows-surprising-potential-to-prevent-cancer-spread-7863881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fans%20SLAM%20Shehnaaz%20for%20her%20'You%20can't%20afford%20me'%20remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741272962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118763109%2Cimgsize-85348.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffans-slam-shehnaaz-gill-for-her-you-cant-afford-me-comment-in-viral-video-even-if-it-was-a-joke-%2Farticleshow%2F118763109.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118763109.cm