ced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20administration's%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20peace%2C%20he%20warned%20that%20any%20attempt%20to%20disturb%20communal%20harmony%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20spokesperson%20Sharvendra%20Bikram%20Singh%20condemned%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20officers%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20act%20as%20BJP%20agents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20officers%20are%20imitating%20what%20they%20hear%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20stay%20in%20his%20good%20books.%20Action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20make%20such%20statements%20and%20openly%20display%20their%20bias.%20This%20is%20condemnable%2C%20and%20officers%20should%20not%20act%20as%20BJP%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Media%20Committee%20Vice%20Chairman%20Manish%20Hindvi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20officer%2C%20regardless%20of%20who%20they%20are%2C%20must%20be%20secular%3B%20only%20then%20can%20governance%20function%20properly%20in%20this%20country.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20anarchy.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20from%20a%20particular%20religion%20have%20expressed%20discomfort%20with%20the%20playing%20with%20colours%2C%20the%20officer's%20duty%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20or%20insecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20an%20arrangement%20where%20both%20Holi%20is%20celebrated%20and%20Namaz%20is%20offered%20peacefully.%20Saying%20that%20Holi%20comes%20once%20a%20year%20while%20Friday%20prayers%20happen%2052%20times%20and%20that%20those%20who%20dislike%20colours%20should%20stay%20indoors%20is%20a%20political%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20engage%20in%20vote-bank%20politics%20make%20such%20remarks.%20As%20an%20officer%2C%20one%20cannot%20make%20such%20statements%3B%20otherwise%2C%20tomorrow%20they%20might%20say%20