ians%20who%20study%20engineering%2C%20as%20these%20men%20and%20I%20did%2C%20end%20up%20living%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20if%20not%20the%20actual%20Silicon%20Valley.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20you%20only%20realise%20the%20value%20of%20something%20once%20you've%20lost%20it.%20That%20happened%20with%20each%20of%20these%20people%2C%20who%20seem%20more%20special%20now%20than%20they%20ever%20did%20before.%20But%20their%20lovability%20and%20eligibility%20may%20also%20be%20exaggerated%20by%20the%20simple%20fact%20that%20I%20already%20know%20them.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20made%20it%20through%20the%20initial%20unknowing%20and%20courtship%2C%20through%20%E2%80%98making%20it%20official'%20and%20the%20honeymoon%20period%2C%20through%20subsequent%20times%20of%20conflict%2C%20boredom%2C%20or%20just%20happiness%2C%20sometimes%20for%20years%2C%20until%20something%20or%20the%20other%20gave%20way.%20And%20we%20still%20had%20love%20for%20each%20other%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20We%20Keep%20Going%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20faced%20with%20the%20task%20of%20selecting%20a%20%E2%80%98life%20partner'%20from%20a%20sea%20of%20people%20I%20have%20nothing%20in%20common%20with%2C%20familiarity%20could%20never%20breed%20contempt.%20Familiarity%20now%20means%20safety%20(they%20won't%20kill%20me!)%2C%20comfort%20(they%20already%20know%20me!)%2C%20a%20certain%20automatic%20release%20of%20love%2C%20gratitude%2C%20inside%20jokes%2C%20even%20an%20appreciation%20for%20my%20own%20life%2C%20because%20of%20its%20depth%20and%20history%20(somebody%20actually%20loved%20me%20for%20years%20and%20I%20them!%20mad!).%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20why%20we%20still%20long%20for%20love%20lost%20even%20when%20inundated%20with%20endless%20options%20on%20dating%20apps.%20(Those%20remaining%20exes%20in%20SF%20might%20be%20the%20ones%20to%20go%20after%20next%2C%20who%20knows!)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamiliarity%20is%20now%20the%20antidote%20to%20hours%20of%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20new%20person%20to%20know%20you%2C%20warts%20and%20all%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20with%20the%20mad%20hope%20of%20being%20understood%20and%20seen%20by%20a%20complete%20stranger.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20investment%20is%20worth%20anything%2C%20or%20will%20ever%20succeed.%20And%20try%20as%20I%20might%20to%20detach%20the%20process%20from%20its%20desired%20outcome%2C%20of%20ending%20up%20in%20a%20meaningful%20relationship%2C%20the%20process%20itself%20often%20disappoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20people%20I%20met%20on%20the%20apps%20who%20became%20some%20of%20my%20good%20friends%20in%20the%20city%2C%20even%20if%20we%20decided%20not%20to%20date.%20But%20equally%20often%20occur%20experiences%20so%20sour%20that%20they%20make%20you%20question%20the%20very%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdating%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20your%20foolish%20hope%20of%20finding%20someone%20%E2%80%98special'.%20Why%20else%20would%20the%20universe%20make%20you%20wade%20through%20so%20many%20unpleasant%20experiences%2C%20if%20not%20to%20tell%20you%20to%20give%20up%20on%20your%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20One%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatience%20As%20A%20Gift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20the%20time%20I%20met%20this%20man%20I%20grew%20increasingly%20unsure%20of%E2%80%94he%20insisted%20on%20choosing%20the%20place%2C%20he%20ordered%20most%20of%20the%20food%2C%20but%20also%20indicated%20he'd%20like%20to%20pay%E2%80%94and%20after%20I%20said%20I%20wouldn't%20like%20to%20meet%20again%2C%20he%20insisted%20I%20pay%20him%20back%20(just%20don't%20offer%20to%20pay%20in%20the%20first%20place!%20Why%20make%20flimsy%20offers%20you%20won't%20stand%20by%20later%3F)%20Then%20there%20was%20another%20promising%20prospect%E2%80%94he%20was%20cute%2C%20and%20we'd%20been%20texting%20intensely%20for%20days%E2%80%94when%2C%20suddenly%2C%20just%20as%20we%20were%20deciding%20where%20to%20meet%2C%20he%20went%20silent.%20I%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20block%20him%E2%80%94that%20was%20better%20than%20sitting%20around%20and%20looking%20at%20my%20phone%20for%20hours%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20reply%20I%20was%20due%E2%80%94but%20it%20was%20still%20a%20tattered%20bandage%20over%20my%20yet%20again%20dashed%20hopes.%20There%20was%20another%20man%20who%20decided%2C%20a%20few%20silent%20weeks%20after%20some%20initial%20meetings%2C%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwasn't%20in%20a%20place%20to%20start%20something%20new%E2%80%9D.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20guy%20who%2C%20after%20a%20week%20of%20banter%2C%20chemistry%2C%20and%20regular%20talking%2C%20stopped%20replying%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20wanted%20in%20any%20relationship%2C%20in%20principle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20far%20from%20properly%20liking%20any%20of%20these%20people.%20But%20the%20hurt%20isn't%20so%20much%20heartache%20as%20it%20is%20from%20impatience%20and%20loss%20of%20faith.%20Each%20time%20the%20premise%20of%20the%20dating%20app%20is%20violated%E2%80%94that%20people%20will%20at%20least%20try%20to%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%20sincerely%3B%20that%20the%20obstacle%20to%20a%20real%20relationship%20will%20be%20incompatibility%20or%20other%20issues%20discovered%20over%20time%2C%20not%20%E2%80%98unprofessionalism'%2C%20dishonesty%2C%20and%20uncouth%20behaviour%20ad%20infinitum%E2%80%94you%20lose%20the%20energy%20to%20believe%2C%20to%20be%20emotionally%20invested%20and%20decent%20yourself.%20And%20if%20you%20think%20it's%20only%20women%20who're%20dealing%20with%20stupid%20men%2C%20there's%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20men%2C%20too%2C%20are%20sick%20of%20being%20cancelled%20upon%20and%20treated%20badly.%20The%20%E2%80%98Women-in-Male-Dominated-Fields'%20trend%2C%20however%2C%20which%20are%20memes%20based%20on%20women%20being%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20flake%20or%20lose%20interest%20in%20a%20guy%2C%20also%20suggests%20that%20is%20just%20women%20retaliating%20by%20finally%20giving%20men%20a%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20all-too-convenient%20medicine%20of%20losing%20fucks%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat.%20God%20knows%20I've%20lost%20interest%20in%20people%20I%20just%20started%20talking%20to%2C%20perhaps%20because%20of%20who%20they%20were%2C%20or%20because%20life%20got%20in%20the%20way%2C%20or%20because%20I%20stopped%20seeing%20the%20value%20in%20trying%20harder%20than%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHurt%2C%20Hurt%20Everywhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20incentive%20to%20muster%20the%20courage%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20know-how%20to%20deal%20with%20strangers%20politely%E2%80%94unlike%20with%20people%20you've%20known%20for%20a%20while.%20A%20friend%20in%20the%20same%20predicament%20as%20me%20believes%20that%20we%20live%20in%20a%20generation%20of%20hurt%20people%20hurting%20other%20people%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20hurting%20themselves%E2%80%94while%20perhaps%20hurting%20themselves%20anyway.%20That%20technology%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20this%20apathy%3F%E2%80%94malaise%3F%20insincerity%3F%20self-preservation%3F%E2%80%94is%20a%20common%20diagnosis%2C%20one%20that%20I%20partially%20believe%20in.%20Dating%20apps%20have%20famously%20ruined%20love%3A%20by%20compressing%20people%20into%20six%20pictures%20and%20some%20boilerplate%20%E2%80%98witty'%20text%2C%20and%20making%20you%20think%20endlessly%20about%20these%20ideas%20of%20yourself%20and%20another%2C%20until%20the%20many-sided%20humanity%20of%20everyone%20involved%20becomes%20moot%3B%20by%20having%20a%20business%20model%20fundamentally%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20problem%20it's%20trying%20to%20solve%E2%80%94for%20every%20couple%20it%20creates%2C%20a%20dating%20app%20loses%20not%20one%20but%20two%20%E2%80%98users'%3B%20by%20dangling%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%98perfect'%20connection%20at%20every%20turn%2C%20so%20if%20you%20find%20one%20thing%20you%20don't%20like%20about%20someone%2C%20you%20can%20just%20discard%20them%20and%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next.%20Soon%20our%20%E2%80%9CAI%20concierges%E2%80%9D%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20dating%20hundreds%20of%20other%20%E2%80%9CAI%20concierges%E2%80%9D%20on%20our%20behalf%2C%20to%20narrow%20us%20down%20to%20the%20evermore%20%E2%80%9Cperfect%E2%80%9D%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstagram%20seems%20to%20be%20reading%20between%20the%20lines%20of%20my%20WhatsApp%20chats%2C%20surfacing%20content%20that%20addresses%20these%20personal%20questions.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20someone%20can't%20meet%20your%20needs%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20why.%20Walk%20away%20and%20don't%20compromise%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20doesn't%20deserve%20you%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20right%20man%20will%20chase%20you%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CBe%20in%20your%20divine%20feminine.%20Cut%20people%20off%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20You%20Love%20Yourself%20A%20Little%20Too%20Much%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20tremendously%20confused%20about%20whether%20this%20emphasis%20on%20self-protection%2C%20disguised%20as%20self-care%2C%20is%20really%20in%20service%20to%20us%20not%20abandoning%20ourselves%20(which%20is%20advice%20I%20could%20really%20use%2C%20frankly)%E2%80%94or%20is%20it%20more%20of%20the%20hyper-individualism%20that%20we%20deem%20necessary%20to%20a%20healthy%20self-concept%20today%3F%20They%20say%20growth%20happens%20in%20the%20difficult%2C%20messy%20spaces%20of%20human%20connection%3B%20your%20ego%20may%20not%20feel%20like%20it's%20%E2%80%9Cwinning%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20you're%20being%20forced%20to%20change%20anyway.%20I%20wonder%20if%20the%20frequent%20conflation%20of%20compromise%20and%20%E2%80%98settling'%20with%20weakness%20or%20loss%20is%20creating%20a%20generation%20of%20emotionally%20stunted%E2%80%94endlessly%20seeking%20and%20isolated%E2%80%94people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20we%20actually%20do%3F%20Well%2C%20if%20I%20knew%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20trying%20to%20wring%20value%20from%20all%20my%20romantic%20failures%20in%20public.%20So%20now%20might%20be%20the%20time%20for%20you%20to%20stop%20reading%E2%80%94unless%20you're%20okay%20with%20less%20value%2C%20more%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20answer%20in%20arranged%20marriages%20after%20all%2C%20which%20filters%20for%20seriousness%20of%20intent%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20integrity%3F%20I%20did%20make%20a%20Shaadi.com%20profile%20once%2C%20but%20the%20crowd%20there%20seemed%20so%20besmirched%20by%20people%20doing%20it%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%2C%20with%20an%20app%20interface%20that%20took%20me%20back%20to%201995%20and%20spam%20calls%20from%20suitors%20that%20put%20NoBroker%20to%20shame%2C%20that%20I%20didn't%20think%20anyone%20I'd%20love%20could%20be%20there.%20I%20uninstalled%20it%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20I%20simply%20give%20up%20on%20both%20the%20process%20and%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20instead%20do%20things%20I%20love%20with%20the%20time%20recovered%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdating%20overhead%E2%80%9D%3F%20Perhaps%20I'll%20meet%20someone%20cool%20then.%20If%20not%2C%20I'll%20at%20least%20have%20spent%20my%20time%20the%20way%20I%20like%20to%2C%20and%20make%20more%20progress%20on%20things%20that%20are%20actually%20under%20my%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20those%20remaining%20exes%20in%20SF%E2%80%94do%20I%20actually%20come%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Internal%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20real%20remedy%2C%20apart%20from%20making%20jokes%20about%20it%2C%20is%20internal%20and%20emotional.%20The%20%E2%80%98engineering'%20metaphor%20seems%20to%20last%3A%20the%20proportion%20of%20people%20who%20are%20happily%20married%20is%20probably%20comparable%20to%20those%20students%20who%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%20colleges%3B%20yet%2C%20nearly%20everyone%20sits%20the%20exams%20with%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20self-belief%2C%20at%20least%20in%20theory%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20it.%20Only%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20consumed%20by%20studies%20more%20than%20trying%20to%20meet%20people%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I'd%20like.%20But%20the%20odds%20of%20finding%20a%20partner%20are%20also%20better%20than%20succeeding%20in%20an%20education%20system%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20overall%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20resilience%20and%20detachment%20learnt%20in%20those%20teenage%20days%20would%20be%20the%20more%20necessary%20and%20valuable%20tenets%20to%20channel%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framachandranesk%5C%22%3ESanjana%20Ramachandran%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Framachandranesk%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_via%26utm_content%3Dprofile%26utm_medium%3Dios_app%5C%22%3Ewriter%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20marketer%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%C2%A0with%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22NotApplicable%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fx.com%252Framachandranesk%252Fstatus%252F1698942175034433863%26data%3D05%257C02%257CharshitaM%2540ndtv.com%257Cb4a635aa33544c61fff408dd5ca55700%257C89e0013190cd478790cc5ded788d77de%257C0%257C0%257C638768587388545087%257CUnknown%257CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%253D%253D%257C0%257C%257C%257C%26sdata%3DXVBoLsfNnssBE7%252BG7jYWj%252FIPbpNJq6qmcH%252F41LBwGzs%253D%26reserved%3D0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Original%20URL%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Framachandranesk%2Fstatus%2F1698942175034433863.%20Click%20or%20tap%20if%20you%20trust%20this%20link.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebook%20from%20Aleph%20coming%20out%20soon.%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A174126456000