%20officials%20have%20said%20the%2014.2%20kg%20haul%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20gold%20seizures%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%2C%20the%20stepdaughter%20of%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Ramachandra%20Rao%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20night%20by%20the%20officers%20of%20DRI.%20The%20agency%2C%20which%C2%A0operates%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%2C%20had%20been%20monitoring%20her%20movements%20due%20to%20her%20frequent%20trips%20to%20Dubai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Customs%20sought%20four-day%20custody%20of%20the%2033-year-old%20actor%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20her%20bail%20petition.%C2%A0Objecting%20to%20this%2C%20her%20lawyer%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ranya-rao-kannada-actor-arrested-on-gold-smuggling-charges-7851786%5C%22%3ERanya%20Rao%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20(from%20March%204%20to%20March%2018)%20as%20the%20DRI%20had%20no%20further%20questions%20for%20her.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20when%20she%20has%20moved%20a%20bail%20petition%2C%20the%20Custom%20department%20needs%20her%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%20The%20court%20has%20reserved%20the%20custody%20order%20for%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lakhs%20In%20Commission%20For%20Smuggling%201%20Kg%20Gold'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20has%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Rao%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20gold%20smuggling%20network%20and%20took%20hefty%20commissions%20to%20smuggle%20goods%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20Indo-Asian%20News%20Service.%20The%20actor%20allegedly%20received%20around%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%20commission%20to%20smuggle%20one%20kilogram%20of%20gold%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20seizure%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%C2%A0searches%20were%20conducted%20at%20Ranya%20Rao's%20home%20and%20gold%20jewellery%20worth%20Rs%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202.67%20crore%20were%20also%20recovered%2C%20the%20DRI%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20interception%2C%20DRI%20officers%20searched%20her%20residence%20on%20Lavelle%20Road%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20lives%20with%20her%20husband.%20The%20search%20led%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20gold%20jewellery%20worth%20Rs%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202.67%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BShocked%20And%20Devastated%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistancing%20himself%20from%20the%20case%2C%20the%20actor's%20stepfather%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20Ms%20Rao%20and%20her%20husband's%20business%20dealings%20and%20that%20the%20law%20would%20take%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BLike%20any%20other%20father%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20and%20devastated%20when%20it%20came%20to%20my%20notice%20through%20the%20media.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20of%20these%20things.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20anything%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Director-General%20of%20Police-rank%20officer%20also%20clarified%20that%20Ms%20Rao%20was%20not%20living%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20living%20separately%20with%20her%20husband.%20There%20must%20be%20some%20problem%20between%20them...%20(maybe)%20due%20to%20some%20family%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20is%20currently%20serving%20as%20the%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Police%20Housing%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'4%20Dubai%20Trips%20In%2015%20Days'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Ms%20Rao%20arrived%20from%20Dubai%20on%20an%20Emirates%20flight.%20Authorities%20grew%20suspicious%20after%20noticing%20that%20she%20had%20travelled%20to%20Dubai%20four%20times%20in%2015%20days%2C%20prompting%20a%20targeted%20operation%20upon%20her%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20allegedly%20smuggled%20the%20gold%20by%20wearing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20it%20and%20concealing%20gold%20bars%20in%20her%20clothing%2C%20investigators%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20into%20the%20case%20also%20suggest%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bused%20her%20connections%26quot%3B%20to%20bypass%20security%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20special%20court%20for%20financial%20offences%2C%20which%20remanded%20her%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20March%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20are%20investigating%20whether%20she%20was%20acting%20alone%20or%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20smuggling%20network%20operating%20between%20Dubai%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanya%20Rao%2C%20who%20has%20appeared%20in%20several%20South%20Indian%20films%2C%20featured%20opposite%20Kannada%20superstar%20Sudeep%20in%20'Maanikya'%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741260240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frrlpqps_actor-ranya-rao-_650x400_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-ranya-rao-arrested-for-smuggling-gold-visited-uae-27-times-in-a-year-7861683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20Arrested%20For%20Smuggling%20Gold%2C%20Visited%20UAE%2027%20Times%20In%20A%20Year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-ranya-rao-arrested-for-smuggling-gold-visited-uae-27-times-in-a-year-7861683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%3A%20Director%20Motwane%20On%20Why%20You%20Can't%20Call%20Lootera%20A%20Flop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVikramaditya%20Motwane's%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20a%20tragic%20letter%20to%20forbidden%20love%E2%80%94the%20pain%20that%20lingers%2C%20the%20loss%20that%20wanders%2C%20and%20the%20love%20that%20speaks%20volumes%20without%20having%20to%20say%20anything%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonakshi%20Sinha%20and%20Ranveer%20Singh%20were%20just%20three%20years%20old%20in%20the%20movie%20business.%20Vikramaditya%20Motwane%20imagined%20a%20vintage%20world%20with%20Pakhi%20(Sonakshi)%20and%20Varun%20(Ranveer).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20set%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%201950s%2C%20when%20newly%20independent%20India's%20Zamindari%20Abolition%20Act%20had%20just%20come%20into%20force.%20Ranveer%20Singh%20played%20the%20role%20of%20a%20conman%20named%20Varun%2C%20while%20Sonakshi%20was%20Pakhi%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20Bengali%20zamindar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Instagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Instagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F3deerah_lootera_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInstagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13%20years%20later%2C%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20to%20re-release%20on%20March%207%2C%202025%2C%20the%20film%20is%20being%20re-released%20by%20PVR%20INOX.%20With%20the%20ongoing%20trend%20of%20re-releases%2C%20%3Cem%3ELootera's%3C%2Fem%3E%20return%20to%20the%20big%20screen%20reaffirms%20the%20love%20it%20found%20years%20after%20its%20original%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20declared%20a%20flop%20film%20back%20in%20the%20day.%20However%2C%20Motwane%20begs%20to%20disagree.%20Why%3F%20Because%20no%20one%20lost%20any%20money%20on%20that%20film%2C%20says%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%20And%3Cem%3E%20Lootera%20%3C%2Fem%3EAren't%20The%20Same%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikramaditya%20Motwane%20highlights%20the%20painstaking%20tendency%20of%20the%20audience%20or%20trends%20in%20the%20movie%20business%2C%20where%20they%20believe%20that%20if%20a%20film%20has%20a%20star%20cast%2C%20it%20must%20cross%20a%20certain%20number%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20And%20if%20it%20doesn't%3F%20Then%20the%20film%20is%20immediately%20put%20in%20the%20box%20of%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20you%20can't%20have%20the%20same%20benchmark%20put%20together%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20terms%20of%2C%20say%2C%20Ranveer%20Singh.%20The%20two%20films%20have%20the%20same%20stars%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20you%20know%20they%20cannot%20be%20judged%20on%20the%20same%20benchmark.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20more%20from%20that%20perspective%20that%20Sonakshi%20did%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20her%20commercial%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EDabangg%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESon%20of%20Sardar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20Ranveer%20while%20doing%20%3Cem%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3ELadies%20Vs%20Ricky%20Bahl%20-%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0these%20are%20commercial%20films%20and%20hence%20will%20get%20commercial%20numbers.%20But%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20not%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Sonakshi%20Being%20Asked%20To%20Not%20Go%20For%20An%20Arty%20Film%20So%20Early%20In%20Her%20Career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%2C%20Sonakshi%20revealed%20how%20she%20was%20repeatedly%20asked%20to%20think%20twice%20before%20doing%20an%20%26quot%3Barty%26quot%3B%20film%20like%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20has%20a%20very%20limited%20audience%20in%20its%20periphery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20logic%20behind%20it.%20Why%20shouldn't%20she%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F3runtpro_lootera_625x300_06_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotwane%20elaborates%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20said%20that%20you%20should%20make%20a%20film%20for%20forever%3B%20not%20just%20for%20now.%20The%20longevity%20of%20the%20film%20should%20be%20beyond%20just%20those%20two%20months%20after%20its%20release.%20Today%2C%20if%20you%20see%20Sonakshi%20or%20Ranveer's%20filmography%2C%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20at%20the%20very%20top%20of%20it.%20And%20does%20that%20not%20showcase%20their%20versatility%20and%20range%3F%20That's%20how%20stars%20stay%20as%20stars%20in%20public%20memory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeirdest%20Review%20Of%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0opened%20to%20a%20barrage%20of%20reviews%3B%20a%20fair%20mix%20of%20positive%20and%20negative.%20But%20out%20of%20the%20many%20reviews%20that%20truly%20applauded%20Sonakshi%20and%20Ranveer's%20performances%2C%20and%20Vikramaditya%20Motwane's%20artistic%20vision%2C%20one%20particularly%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotwane%20laughs%20as%20he%20shares%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20there%20was%20one%20review%20where%20the%20film%20got%20five%20stars.%20But%20the%20reviewer%20wrote%20a%20whole%20paragraph%20about%20Sonakshi's%20nose.%20And%20I%20remember%20Sonakshi%20reacting%20very%20positively%2C%20'What%20does%20this%20mean%3F%20Why%20write%20a%20paragraph%20about%20my%20nose%3F'%20It%20was%20a%20beautiful%20review%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20we%20were%20quite%20tickled%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20underwhelming%20response%20bother%20relatively%20newbies%20like%20Ranveer%20and%20Sonakshi%20back%20then%3F%20They%20were%20yet%20to%20taste%20the%20lows%20of%20a%20film's%20average%20reception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20reacts%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20were%20upset%20about%20the%20reviews.%20I%20think%20more%20about%20the%20reception%20of%20the%20film%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20significant%20one.%20I%20think%20Sonakshi%20found%20it%20ironic%20that%20she%20wasn't%20considered%20for%20an%20award%20for%20a%20film%20that%20was%20one%20of%20her%20finest%20performances.%20But%20I%20think%20they%20also%20had%20their%20heads%20on%20their%20shoulders%20and%20knew%20that%20it%20is%20a%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20that%20you%20have%20to%20move%20on%20quickly%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we%20all%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERanveer%20Singh%20And%20Sonakshi%20Sinha%20Off%20Camera%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ranveer%20Singh%20has%20successfully%20achieved%20the%20title%20of%20a%20firecracker%20in%20the%20industry.%20So%2C%20how%20were%20Ranveer%20and%20Sonakshi%20when%20the%20cameras%20weren't%20rolling%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20sets%2C%20we%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotwane%20shares%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20remember%20I%20had%20to%20go%20and%20take%20away%20Ranveer's%20coffee.%20Precisely%20why%20you%20said%20that%20-%20because%20he's%20so%20high%20on%20energy.%20I%20told%20him%20that's%20it.%20And%20funnily%2C%20it%20was%20he%20who%20said%20that%20he'd%20go%20for%20green%20tea%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Instagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Instagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F83rtnud_ranveer-singh_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInstagram%2FVikramaditya%20Motwane%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Sonakshi%2C%20the%20director%20continues%2C%20%26quot%3BShe's%20lovely.%20There%20was%20a%20particular%20scene%20that%20we%20were%20shooting%20in%20a%20car%20where%20she%20gets%20an%20injection.%20Because%20we%20were%20stuck%20in%20that%20car%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20she%20got%20so%20irritated%20that%20she%20cribbed%2C%20'I%20want%20to%20go%20home'%2C%20what%20you%20don't%20see%20is%20how%20she%20changes%20when%20the%20light%20goes%20off%20and%20then%20comes%20on.%20She%20would%20be%20complaining%20when%20it%20went%20off%2C%20and%20then%20suddenly%20smiling%20when%20it%20came%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fdtjtc628_lootera_625x300_06_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Sonakshi%20And%20Ranveer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20Sonakshi%20in%20her%20debut%20film%20%3Cem%3EDabangg%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20her%20eyes%20were%20absolutely%20beautiful.%20I%20think%20she%20was%20phenomenal.%20As%20for%20Ranveer%2C%20%3Cem%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20know%20that%20he%20is%20actually%20from%20Bombay%20and%20not%20Delhi%2C%20such%20was%20the%20conviction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikramaditya%20Motwane's%20debut%20directorial%20%3Cem%3EUdaan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20Sonakshi%20Sinha%20and%20Ranveer%20Singh's%20debut%20films%3B%20%3Cem%3EDabangg%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%20respectively%3B%20were%20released%20in%20the%20same%20year%E2%80%942010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20destiny%20might%20have%20it%2C%20their%20paths%20crossed%20when%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20being%20planned%20and%20prepped.%20And%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Most%20Spontaneous%20And%20Toughest%20Scenes%20From%20The%20Film%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20times%2C%20it's%20the%20spontaneity%20of%20the%20actor%20that%20makes%20an%20ordinary%20scene%20extraordinary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Cem%3ELootera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20happens%20when%20Varun%20(Ranveer)%20has%20to%20force%20Pakhi%20(Sonakshi)%20to%20take%20her%20injection.%20Sonakshi's%20character%20battles%20chronic%20tuberculosis%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikramaditya%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20to%20force%20her%20into%20a%20corner%20and%20struggle%20to%20make%20her%20take%20the%20injection.%20And%20when%20we%20were%20there%20at%20that%20house%20in%20Dalhousie%2C%20the%20scene%20was%20initially%20written%20as%20something%20that%20had%20to%20be%20done%20in%20one%20place.%20But%20then%20we%20thought%20why%20not%20try%20it%20this%20way%2C%20show%20the%20whole%20struggle%20and%20that%20somehow%20made%20the%20scene%20dynamic.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20because%20the%20two%20leads%20were%20just%20hitting%20each%20other%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20director%20recollects%20how%20the%20entire%20film%20was%20a%20challenge%20from%20the%20production%20standpoint.%20Everything%20that%20could%20go%20wrong%2C%20did%20go%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20shares%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20start%20off%20in%20Dalhousie%20and%20we%20weren't%20getting%20snow%20and%20suddenly%20we%20got%20the%20highest%20snowfall%20in%2040%20years%20in%20that%20place%20and%20then%20when%20we%20built%20the%20set%2C%20it%20collapsed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20moved%20the%20entire%20production%20from%20Dalhousie%20to%20Bengal%20to%20shoot%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20film.%20Weren't%20ready%20for%20that.%20Then%20eventually%20we%20came%20and%20shot%20the%20whole%20sequence%20in%20May%3B%20it%20was%20crazy.%20But%20I%20think%20the%20most%20challenging%20part%20was%20the%20cru