20take%20the%20plunge%2C%20contacting%20Shubham%20and%20flying%20to%20Nusa%20Penida%2C%20Bali%2C%20to%20train%20with%20him.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20big%20leap%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20I%20needed%20to%20evolve%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%20Scuba%20diving%2C%20while%20enjoyable%2C%20felt%20too%20assisted.%20For%20Archana%2C%20free%20diving%2C%20with%20its%20emphasis%20on%20breath-hold%20and%20self-reliance%2C%20offered%20a%20deeper%2C%20more%20challenging%20connection%20with%20the%20ocean.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%2C%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20my%20lungs%20take%20me%20deeper%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20muses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScuba%20diving%20was%20also%20saturated%2C%20and%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20male-dominated%20industry%2C%20she%20knew%20she%20needed%20to%20do%20something%20unique%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-90_11zon-1740397134-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22archana%20sankaranarayanan%20freediving%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-90_11zon-1740397134-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-90_11zon-1740397134-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-90_11zon-1740397134-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-90_11zon-1740397134.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-409002%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchana%20felt%20obligated%20to%20the%20sea%20and%20wanted%20to%20stay%20underwater%20as%20